4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence that is designed for professionals who want to leverage AI in their current roles. The course lasts for 6 weeks and includes 2 live online classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people maximum. No previous experience is required to take this course. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course covers various topics such as generative AI, context, prompts, and models. By the end of the course, students will be equipped with the necessary tools and best practices to implement AI strategically and enhance their workplace capabilities. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop